The paper deals with multi-modal neural machine translation, which involves both natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP. The paper also involves CV techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of a latent variable model and machine learning techniques suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves artificial intelligence (AI) techniques, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with multi-modal translation, which suggests that it could belong to cs.MM (Multimedia).
